data.text:
San José de Las Matas

San José de Las Matas is a city in Santiago Province, in Dominican Republic.

GPS Coordinates of San José de Las Matas, Santiago Province, Dominican Republic

San José de Las Matas is located on the latitude of 19.33915 and longitude of -70.93819 and has a geohash of d7mw1b86sqge.

Cities and Towns near San José de Las Matas

The nearest significant population center from San José de Las Matas is Río Verde Arriba in La Vega Province, Dominican Republic, located 39 kilometers or 24 miles → E of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Jarabacoa (La Vega Province, Dominican Republic) located 40 km (24 mi) → E and Concepción de La Vega (La Vega Province, Dominican Republic) located 44 km (27 mi) → E of San José de Las Matas.

In total, we found 50 cities near San José de Las Matas in our database.
